title: WordCamp Houston 2010 Keynote MP4 Re-Encode
description:
MP4 re-encode of the keynote speech from WordCamp Houston 2010 at the Houston Museum of Natural Science, 2010 August 7.

Contents:

pre-introduction by Monica Danna (the event's lead organizer, co.lab)
introduction by Dwight Silverman (Houston Chronicle, Technology Bytes)
keynote by Matt Mullenweg (Automattic, founder of the WordPress project)

This is the same video as the FLV version, with a title sequence added at the beginning and upsampled to full NTSC resolution for broader compatibility
